{"tid":1719372,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔好睇少張建宗新招，再落去好快變‘政府帶領市民’ 鬥 黑衣人（佢哋會叫暴徒）","createTime":"2019-11-14T05:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T22:23:14.000Z","uid":48083,"like":83,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"00b52c2fd5e8716142f426ded12730165a49771c","tid":1719372,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:34:31.000Z","msg":"1. 運動不斷循環：<br />\n政府出錯/警暴<br />\n&mdash;》升級<br />\n&mdash;〉有人埋怨不便，政府轉打民意牌<br />\n&mdash;》政府又出錯；<br />\n<br />\n依家又到&lsquo;出現民怨&lsquo;階段<br />\n<br />\n2. 目標係追究殺人強姦責任<br />\n但不論文宣同報紙都越來越少講<br />\n<br />\n請唔好低估香港人記憶力有幾似金魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全社會注意力已去哂堵路同點番工放工<br />\n<br />\n3. 一般市民眼中，堵路既一部分合理性係來自保護中大<br />\n<br />\n但哩方面又似暫時解除咗<br />\n<br />\n4. 民建聯等已經動員<br />\n<br />\n5. 唔好當民意必然一面倒<br />\n今日太子旺角見唔少人自發清路障<br />\n<br />\n所以：<br />\n1. 最好就梗係奉公守法和平處理矛盾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 如果繼續堵，清晰講要求係咩？<br />\n<br />\n覺得&lsquo;全港堵路抗爭&rsquo;既訴求集中喺追究數單殺人強姦事件 同停止警隨意入私人物業 侵犯私產（針對外資）<br />\n因為追究殺人責任  會比 五大訴求有感染力 同 道德高地<br />\n<br />\n3. 依家全港留守太散，好似俾老黑搞<br />\n<br />\n4. 建議明確表明支持民主投票，唔會阻礙區議會當日市民投票既交通路線<br />\n<br />\n新算有人覺得區選唔重要<br />\n但都唔好俾政府將停區選責任推俾示威者<br />\n&lsquo;打住民主旗號反民主&rsquo;，哩頂帽既傷害，好可能比你想像中大<br />\n<br />\n5. 請唔好有權力既傲慢，保持檢視民眾既反應同ai反省學習功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭者一方已實際有使用主要公路既&lsquo;公權力&rsquo;，附之而來有&lsquo;回應訴求&rsquo;既道德責任<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得你啱市民錯，所以幾大反響都唔理，咁同777係冇分別<br />\n<br />\n成日話獨立自冶，咁係咪需要學習如何運用權力？<br />\n<br />\n一正一反兩個例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nnTHhP3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnnTHhP3.png&h=73a67834&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3V4LfBN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3V4LfBN.png&h=8d0c3c3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb5028a11aec0ecb047afe406d0af21f15aff6e0","tid":1719372,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:35:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0dbed5430ebdd763c450c0cfebcdcc9c0245a65c","tid":1719372,"uid":75056,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"玩紅衛兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，著翻普通衫打過囉"},{"pid":"8b78c7b16e0d839a21752f1bfe2b997a9187ca13","tid":1719372,"uid":18484,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:35:57.000Z","msg":"想拖埋全線鈴務員落水"},{"pid":"f06c5a998f3820337fb3602b7737cd9c20f07c5b","tid":1719372,"uid":18484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b78c7b16e0d839a21752f1bfe2b997a9187ca13","tid":1719372,"uid":18484,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:35:57.000Z","msg":"想拖埋全線鈴務員落水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:36:08.000Z","msg":"公務員"},{"pid":"e1d6b3c4fb4d159227483ef2dcdf0e5e2cf63b8a","tid":1719372,"uid":136431,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"政府正式整編白骨團<br />\n遲早會授權埋公民逮捕權畀班撚樣"},{"pid":"ee5623c0949cd342cdd7083cd2cdb40f76c107a1","tid":1719372,"uid":48083,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"e1d6b3c4fb4d159227483ef2dcdf0e5e2cf63b8a","tid":1719372,"uid":136431,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"政府正式整編白骨團<br />\n遲早會授權埋公民逮捕權畀班撚樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"明顯國際壓力太大<br />\n所以依家唔再搞中大<br />\n政府popo唔出面<br />\n用老黑<br />\n打鑊勁popo先出嚟主持正義收拾殘局"},{"pid":"dff74e34cff37fb24e16f272968f0752a26b3684","tid":1719372,"uid":332503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:38:58.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<br />\n但係都tui"},{"pid":"96ebe8ade00b33d33ffdc2aa642dec72b2b86052","tid":1719372,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"cited